# Tauri / Rust build artifacts — regenerated by `cargo`/`tauri build`.
# NEVER commit: src-tauri/target alone is ~3GB.
src-tauri/target/
src-tauri/gen/

# Node (tauri-cli + e2e harness deps)
node_modules/

# E2E run artifacts (isolated WebView2 user-data / logs / reports — all reproducible)
e2e/runs/
e2e/reports/
e2e/rwd-runs/
e2e-screenshot*.png

# NOTE: prebuilt/cim-light.exe IS committed on purpose.
# WDAC (enforced) blocks a local cargo rebuild, so the runnable shell binary
# ships with the repo. Rebuild it only on a non-WDAC machine, then replace this file.
